Additionally, the paper proposes a new structure for CNNs that achieves better performance with fewer parameters. 

The paper also touches upon topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) such as overfitting, parameter redundancy, and network performance. 

Neural Networks (cs.NE) is another likely sub-category as the paper discusses the structure and performance of deep neural networks. 

Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is also a possible sub-category as the paper proposes a new structure for CNNs that improves their performance. 

Finally, Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) is a less likely sub-category as the paper does not explicitly discuss language processing, but it does touch upon topics related to feature aggregation and information flow, which are relevant to NLP.
